<sent type="title" lang="kor" page="3a" n="1">북찬가</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="3" n="2">가련可憐타 묘여일신藐如一身</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="3" n="3">턴지간天地間의 뉘 비比고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="3" n="4">십셰十歲에 조고早孤니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="3" n="5">엄안嚴顔을 안다 가</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="3" n="6">일一生을 영폐永廢니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="3" n="7">군문君門을 라볼가</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="3" n="8">친쳑親戚이 다 이니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="3" n="9">붕우朋友야 니소냐</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="3" n="10">셰군細君조차 포병抱病니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="3" n="11">산生産도 머흘시고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="3" n="12">형뎨兄弟는 본 업고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="3" n="13">계繼子 자 일헤</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="4a" n="1">오륜五倫의 버서나니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="4" n="2">팔八字도 궁독窮獨샤</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="4" n="3">편친偏親만 의지依支여</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="4" n="4">지낙至樂이 이이라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="4" n="5">고孤兒의 두린 </sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="4" n="6">넘  다칠 </sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="4" n="7">과환科宦도 이 업서</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="4" n="8">셰망世網을 피避리라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="4" n="9">경낙京洛치 번화지繁華地</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="4" n="10">젼셩시全盛時의 하딕下直고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="4" n="11">곡海曲으로 깁히 들어</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="4" n="12">암혈에 최이니</sent><!-- 원문에서 찢어진 부분으로 확인 불가-->
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="4" n="13">경화 못 맛나니</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="5a" n="1">인간人間 시비是非 내 아던가</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="5" n="2">지원至願을 일우거냐</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="5" n="3">복지福地가 여긔로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="5" n="4">슉슈菽水 못 니워도</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="5" n="5">슬하膝下의 댱시長侍여</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="5" n="6">훈慈訓을 엄사嚴師 삼아</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="5" n="7">삼쳔교三遷敎 라보고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="5" n="8">아 노롯  노롯</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="5" n="9">유희乳兒戱 일삼으며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="5" n="10">친년親年이 점고漸高니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="5" n="11">원유遠遊를 의意思가</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="6a" n="1">절節祀 길도 못 닐제</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="6" n="2">지정至情이 결연缺然샤</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="6" n="3">집 뒤헤 텬장遷葬고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="6" n="4">됴석朝夕의 쳠瞻拜니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="6" n="5">양養生이며 망事亡매</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="6" n="6">졍녜情禮 거의 펼 </sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="6" n="7">닙신立身 편양便養 못 거니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="6" n="8">힘대로나 밧들니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="6" n="9">후後嗣도 쳐냥凄凉니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="6" n="10">내 몸장 다오려</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="6" n="11">쳔만千萬 근심 다 리고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="6" n="12">여餘生을 즐기러니</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="7a" n="1">경심驚心타 지어앙池魚殃에</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="7" n="2">묵은 불 닐어나니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="7" n="3">삼십여三十餘 년年 눅힌 은젼恩典</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="7" n="4">오날에  면免가</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="7" n="5">향옥鄕獄에 自就여</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="7" n="6">쳐분處分을 기일</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="7" n="7">일白日에 벽녁霹靂 려</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="7" n="8">눈 우희 서리 치니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="7" n="9">눈섭에 러진 厄</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="7" n="10">독의 든 피避넌가</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="7" n="11">일신一身의 화복禍福이야</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="7" n="12">피창彼蒼만 미더신</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="8a" n="1">외로울 우리 편모偏母</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="8" n="2">눌노 여 위안慰安고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="8" n="3">일월日月이 고명高明샤</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="8" n="4">옥셕玉石을 희시니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="8" n="5">특지特旨의  말이</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="8" n="6">명自鳴 더소냐</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="8" n="7">죽은 남기 봄을 만나</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="8" n="8"> 희  도치니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="8" n="9">남찬南竄나 북젹北謫들</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="8" n="10">죄罪가 아냐 영광榮光일</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="8" n="11">투져投杼던 남은 경혼驚魂</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="8" n="12">의녀倚閭고 감읍感泣네</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="9a" n="1">이 군은君恩 이 텬天幸은</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="9" n="2">결초結草 다 갑흘가</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="9" n="3">소素昧에 강도샹江都相도</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="9" n="4">법法 밧긔 측은惻隱커</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="9" n="5">지친至親의 판금오判金五</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="9" n="6">내 언제 져린가</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="9" n="7">불모지不毛地 고 자</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="9" n="8">극북極北에 더지이니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="9" n="9">북당北堂의 미츤 말이</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="9" n="10">놀나온 다多幸</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="9" n="11">험딘險津을 혜지 말고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="9" n="12">듀야晝夜로 녀 와셔</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="10a" n="1"> 밤  나즐</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="10" n="2">손 잡고 작별作別</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="10" n="3">뉵십六十 쇠년衰年 발옹白髮翁이</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="10" n="4">팔질八耋 병친病親 나올 제</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="10" n="5">수쳔數千 니里 限 업 길</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="10" n="6">다시 보기 긔약期約가</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="10" n="7">이 내 졍경情境 이 내 니별離別</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="10" n="8">고금古今의 듯도 못희</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="10" n="9">일日色도 참담慘憺커든</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="10" n="10">텰셕鐵石인 견딀손갸</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="10" n="11">친의親意 딘졍鎭定려</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="10" n="12">모진  둘너 먹고</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="11a" n="1">셜운 간댱肝腸 설이 담아</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="11" n="2">눈물을 고 아</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="11" n="3">하딕下直고 문門을 나니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="11" n="4">가이 터지거다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="11" n="5">팔쳑八尺 댱신長身 설잉구여</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="11" n="6">반부담半負擔의 실녀시니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="11" n="7">챵능참昌陵站 수십니數十里의</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="11" n="8">숑츄松楸 디나갈</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="11" n="9">조훈祖訓을 듯 </sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="11" n="10">혼兒魂이 로 </sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="11" n="11">지원至寃 힌 회포懷抱</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="11" n="12">통곡痛哭 플닐소냐</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="12a" n="1">엄견嚴譴이 유有限니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="12" n="2">경頃刻인 엄뉴淹留가</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="12" n="3">부용 채쳐 몰아</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="12" n="4">십젼구돈十顚九頓 면免소냐</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="12" n="5">양쥬楊州라 노던 희</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="12" n="6">구안면舊顔面이 다 피避고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="12" n="7">쳥화현淸化縣 낫제 들어</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="12" n="8">쥬인主人도 됴타마</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="12" n="9">行色이 볼  업셔</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="12" n="10">간 곳마다 곤욕困辱이라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="12" n="11">자고 새아 가고 가니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="12" n="12">뒤길은 날날 머</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="13a" n="1">보리 비탈 삼일우三日雨에</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="13" n="2">졍삼征衫을 다 적시고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="13" n="3">고산녕高山嶺 계유 올나</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="13" n="4">경국京國을 굽어 보니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="13" n="5">부운浮雲이 폐蔽塞야</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="13" n="6">남북南北을 못 흴다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="13" n="7">냥쳔梁泉寺 자 들어</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="13" n="8">死生을 묵도黙禱고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="13" n="9">젼졍前定을 점검點撿니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="13" n="10">신셰身世도 곤困厄다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="13" n="11">쳥운샹靑雲上 녯 벗이야</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="13" n="12">거使車로 녀신</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="14a" n="1">탈頉 업슨 초원草原客은</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="14" n="2">저 조차 도피逃避</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="14" n="3">말 못 강산江山의 </sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="14" n="4">이 경景色의 눈을 들가</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="14" n="5">낙민누樂民樓 만셰교萬歲橋</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="14" n="6">결의 디나거다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="14" n="7">관남關南 관북關北 갈닌 길흘</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="14" n="8">단쳔端川으로 내여 노코</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="14" n="9">쳥영靑海營 을 쉬워</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="14" n="10">부녕富寧 젹謫行 후邂逅예</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="14" n="11">길쥬吉州 명쳔明川 어드메오</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="14" n="12">경뢰瓊雷 샹망相望 머도 멀샤</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="15a" n="1">안변安邊 참보慘報 경통驚痛다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="15" n="2">도쳥도셜道廳道說 이과져</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="15" n="3">녕남극변嶺南極邊 졔도 가늬</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="15" n="4">□분오녈□分五裂 수졀愁切샤</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="15" n="5">궁황졀막窮荒絶漠 일됴노一條路에</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="15" n="6">□신□身 고혈孤孑 더욱 셟다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="15" n="7">후치厚峙 매덕賣德 무인지無人地</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="15" n="8">구뷔구뷔 쉬여 넘어</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="15" n="9">능귀촌能歸村 더위 잡아</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="15" n="10">호닌역呼獜驛 도라 들어</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="15" n="11">두산白頭山 겻 두고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="15" n="12">녀진국女眞國 남은 터</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="16a" n="1">익가 수풀 헤쳐 내여</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="16" n="2">형극荊棘을 열어시니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="16" n="3">팔면부지八面不知 일향창一鄕傖과</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="16" n="4">셔식棲息을 의탁依託고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="16" n="5">쳑동尺僮을 편지 주어</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="16" n="6">친졍親庭의 도라갈</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="16" n="7">가향家鄕은 한이라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="16" n="8">인니졍人子離情 아득다</sent>
